B%22title%22%3A%22AAP%20vs%20Tihar%20Jail%20On%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Loss%20Of%20Weight%2C%20Drop%20In%20Blood%20Sugar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Tihar%20jail%20administration%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20are%20locked%20in%20a%20heated%20exchange%20over%20the%20health%20condition%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20While%20AAP%20leaders%20have%20claimed%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20is%20rapidly%20losing%20weight%20and%20his%20health%20is%20declining%20in%20prison%2C%20jail%20authorities%20have%20alleged%20such%20a%20narrative%20aims%20to%20browbeat%20the%20prison%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20AAP%20leaders'%20charge%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20lost%208.5%20kg%20since%20he%20went%20to%20prison%20and%20that%20there%20is%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20kill%20him%20behind%20bars%2C%20the%20Tihar%20jail%20administration%20has%20put%20out%20a%20detailed%20update%20on%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20health%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20on%20March%2021%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20linked%20to%20Delhi's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy.%20He%20was%20out%20on%20bail%20briefly%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20then%20returned%20to%20Tihar%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20jail%20authorities%20have%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20weight%20was%2065%20kg%20on%20April%201%2C%20the%20day%20he%20entered%20Tihar's%20Central%20Jail%20No.%202.%20When%20he%20was%20granted%20bail%20on%20May%2010%20after%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20relief%2C%20he%20weighed%2064%20kg.%20When%20he%20surrendered%20again%20-%20June%202%20-%20the%20weight%20was%20recorded%20as%2063.5.%20Currently%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20weighs%2061.5.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20AAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20had%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20weighed%2070%20kg%20when%20he%20was%20arrested%20and%20this%20has%20reduced%20to%2061.5%20kg.%20This%20rapid%20weight%20loss%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20a%20serious%20ailment%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20jail%20authorities%20have%20said%20that%20the%20prison's%20medical%20officer%20has%20said%20that%20the%20loss%20of%20weight%20%26quot%3Bmay%20be%20due%20to%20consumption%20of%20less%20quantity%20of%20food%20or%20low%20calorie%20intake%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20the%20accused%20is%20under%20supervision%20of%20the%20Senior%20Medical%20Officer%2C%20CJ-02%20round%20the%20clock.%20The%20health%20of%20the%20UTP%20(undertrial%20prisoner)%20is%20under%20continuous%20monitoring%20and%20his%20vitals%20are%20being%20checked%20daily.%20The%20UTP%20is%20being%20reviewed%20by%20Jail%20visiting%20Medical%20Specialist%20Doctor%20of%20Tihar%20jail%20for%20complaints%20posed%20by%20him%20and%20is%20administered%20medicines%2C%20if%20required%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20jail%20report%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountering%20AAP%20leaders'%20contention%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20blood%20sugar%20had%20dropped%20multiple%20times%20in%20jail%2C%20the%20jail%20report%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20present%2C%20the%20inmate%20Blood%20Sugar%20is%20being%20monitored%20as%20advised%20from%20the%20medical%20board%20and%20he%20is%20being%20provided%20treatment%20and%20diet%20as%20advised%20from%20the%20medical%20board%2C%20his%20vitals%20are%20within%20normal%20limits%20at%20present.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20jail%20authorities%20have%20said%20the%20AAP%20ministers%20and%20lawmakers%20were%20levelling%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%20allegations%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BSuch%20a%20narrative%2C%20confuses%20and%20misleads%20the%20public%20with%20false%20information%20and%20ulterior%20motives%20with%20intent%20to%20brow-beat%20the%20Prison%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20blood%20pressure%2C%20blood%20sugar%20and%20weight%20are%20being%20regularly%20monitored%2C%20he%20is%20being%20provided%20adequate%20treatment%20for%20all%20his%20ailments%20and%20is%20eating%20home-cooked%20food%20thrice%20a%20day%2C%20the%20jail%20authorities%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20AAP's%20Sanjay%20Singh%20said%20the%20jail%20report%20confirms%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20lost%20weight%20and%20that%20his%20blood%20sugar%20level%20has%20dropped%20multiple%20times.%20%26quot%3BIf%20sugar%20levels%20are%20low%2C%20one%20may%20slip%20into%20coma%20in%20sleep.%20There%20is%20also%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20brain%20stroke%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20has%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20family%2C%20the%20party%20and%20his%20well-wishers%20are%20concerned%20about%20his%20health.%20%26quot%3BThe%20aim%20of%20BJP%20and%20its%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20is%20to%20keep%20him%20in%20jail%20and%20play%20with%20his%20life.%20They%20are%20hatching%20a%20conspiracy%20so%20that%20he%20faces%20some%20serious%20health%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20Delhi%20unit%20has%20hit%20back.%20Virendra%20Sachdeva%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20party%20in%20Delhi%2C%20has%20said%20AAP%20leaders%20are%20enacting%20a%20%26quot%3Bdrama%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bmislead%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20and%20ensure%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20gets%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721021940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Frfkeh2pg_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_12_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftihar-jail-arvind-kejriwal-aap-aap-vs-tihar-jail-on-arvind-kejriwals-loss-of-weight-drop-in-blood-sugar-6108377%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Tihar%20jail%20administration%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20are%20locked%20in%20a%20heated%20exchange%20over%20the%20health%20condition%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftihar-jail-arvind-ke