.com%2F6694528f5439fb59cebd3dc8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221566%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20gesturing%20as%20he%20is%20assisted%20by%20the%20Secret%20Service%20after%20he%20was%20shot%20during%20a%20campaign%20rally%20in%20Pennsylvania.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FBrendan%20McDermid%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Trump%20rally%20shooting%20was%20unsurprising%2C%20says%20Rachel%20Kleinfeld%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20political%20violence.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat's%20because%20lawmakers%20and%20their%20incendiary%20comments%20created%20a%20climate%20of%20violence%2C%20Kleinfeld%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20named%20Marjorie%20Taylor%20Greene%20and%20Lauren%20Boebert%20as%20examples%20of%20people%20who%20helped%20%26quot%3Bnormalized%20violence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPolitical%20leaders%20like%20Rep.%20Marjorie%20Taylor%20Greene%20and%20Rep.%20Lauren%20Boebert%20have%20created%20an%20environment%20in%20the%20US%20where%20violence%20is%20normalized%2C%20a%20political%20violence%20expert%20said%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-butler-pennsylvania-rally-secret-service-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattempted%20assassination%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERachel%20Kleinfeld%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20political%20violence%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2Fmagazine%2F2024%2F07%2F14%2Fhow-to-curb-political-violence-qa-00168105%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Politico%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20thinks%20it's%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20leaders%20like%20Marjorie%20Taylor%20Greene%20or%20Lauren%20Boebert%20or%20so%20on%26quot%3B%20who've%20been%20%26quot%3Bamplifying%20the%20extremes%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKleinfeld%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Carnegie%20Endowment%20for%20International%20Peace%2C%20added%20that%20she%20thoug