.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-group-to-retain-air-india-s-top-management-post-vistara-merger-124071500169_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-group-to-retain-air-india-s-top-management-post-vistara-merger-124071500169_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mumbai%20Hoarding%20Collapse%3A%20Chargesheet%20Flags%20Ignored%20Soft%20Soil%20Warning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20excavator%20operator%20had%20warned%20that%20the%20place%20in%20Mumbai's%20Ghatkopar%20where%20a%20120%20ft%20x120%20ft%20hoarding%20was%20being%20planned%20had%20soft%20soil%2C%20but%20this%20was%20ignored.%20Sixteen%20months%20later%2C%20the%20massive%20billboard%20came%20crashing%20down%20during%20a%20storm%2C%20killing%2017%20people%20and%20injuring%2074%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%203%2C299-page%20chargesheet%20filed%20in%20a%20Mumbai%20court%2C%20the%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20of%20Mumbai%20Crime%20Branch%20has%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20alleged%20collusion%20of%20top%20officials%20in%20Government%20Railway%20Police%20(GRP)%2C%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(BMC)%20and%20Ego%20Media%20Private%20Limited%20that%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20the%20May%2013%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20an%20excavator%20was%20at%20work%20to%20set%20up%20the%20huge%20billboard%20when%20a%20tree%20fell.%20The%20operator%20sensed%20soft%20soil%20and%20recommended%20a%20soil%20check%20so%20that%20building%20plans%20can%20be%20accordingly%20tweaked%20to%20ensure%20stability%20of%20the%20huge%20structure.%20This%20check%20would%20have%20taken%2015%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Ego%20Media%20director%20Bhavesh%20Bhinde%20and%20former%20director%20Jahnavi%20Marathe%20were%20in%20no%20mood%20to%20wait.%20They%20ignored%20the%20warning%20and%20proceeded%20without%20a%20soil%20check%2C%20the%20chargesheet%20has%20said.%20This%20alleged%20negligence%2C%20police%20have%20said%2C%20can%20be%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20illegal%20billboard%20crashing%20during%20the%20storm.%20The%20excavator%20operator%20is%20among%20more%20than%20100%20witnesses%20whose%20statements%20feature%20in%20the%20police%20chargesheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chargesheet%20also%20raises%20serious%20allegations%20against%20IPS%20officer%20Quaiser%20Khalid%20--%20Khalid%20is%20former%20GRP%20Commissioner%20and%20approval%20for%20the%20hoarding%20was%20granted%20during%20his%20tenure%20--%20and%20BMC%20licence%20inspector%20Sunil%20Dalvi.%20The%20plot%20where%20the%20hoarding%20came%20up%20was%20leased%20to%20the%20GRP%2C%20and%20Khalid%20allegedly%20used%20gaps%20in%20law%20to%20award%20the%20hoarding%20to%20Ego%20Media%20without%20a%20tender%20process.%20He%20has%20now%20been%20suspended.%20Dalvi%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20Ego%20Media%20over%20the%20illegal%20hoarding%2C%20but%20withdrew%20it%20later.%20His%20continued%20contact%20with%20Bhinde%20raised%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chilling%20crash%20of%20the%20hoarding%2C%20which%20was%20so%20big%20that%20it%20made%20it%20to%20the%20Limca%20Book%20of%20Records%2C%20put%20the%20spotlight%20on%20how%20rules%20were%20being%20bent%20and%20public%20safety%20ignored%20while%20granting%20approval%20to%20illegal%20hoardings%20in%20the%20Maximum%20City.%20According%20to%20rules%2C%20the%20maximum%20size%20of%20hoardings%20is%2040%20ft%20x%2040%20ft%2C%20but%20the%20Ghatkopar%20billboard%20was%20thrice%20the%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20has%20told%20the%20assembly%20that%20there%20are%20a%20total%20of%201%2C025%20hoardings%20in%20BMC%20areas%20and%20none%20of%20them%20are%20illegal.%20He%20has%20said%20hoardings%20at%20Railway%20authority's%20land%20are%20not%20erected%20after%20taking%20permission%20from%20BMC.%20According%20to%20a%20BMC%20survey%2C%2