%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fforeign-banks-snapping-up-short-term-indian-bonds-bank-of-america-124071500074_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fforeign-banks-snapping-up-short-term-indian-bonds-bank-of-america-124071500074_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fforeign-banks-snapping-up-short-term-indian-bonds-bank-of-america-124071500074_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Secret%20Service%20Faces%20Scrutiny%20After%20Trump%20Assassination%20Attempt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Secret%20Service%20was%20under%20intense%20scrutiny%20on%20Sunday%20after%20a%20gunman%20managed%20to%20evade%20its%20agents%20and%20open%20fire%20on%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20at%20a%20political%20rally%2C%20with%20Republican%20leaders%20vowing%20swift%20investigations%20and%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20calling%20for%20an%20independent%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gunman%2C%20a%2020-year-old%20Pennsylvania%20man%2C%20injured%20Trump%20and%20killed%20a%20rally%20attendee%20from%20a%20rooftop%20perch%20around%20150%20yards%20(140%20m)%20from%20the%20stage%20where%20the%20former%20president%20was%20speaking%20in%20Butler%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20near%20Pittsburgh%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%2078%2C%20who%20like%20other%20former%20presidents%20has%20lifetime%20protection%20by%20the%20Secret%20Service%2C%20was%20swarmed%20by%20agents%20who%20then%20rushed%20him%20away.%20Agents%20killed%20the%20shooter%2C%20identified%20by%20the%20FBI%20as%20Thomas%20Matthew%20Crooks%20of%20Bethel%20Park%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20and%20an%20AR-15-style%20semiautomatic%20was%20recovered%20near%20his%20body%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20says%20a%20bullet%20hit%20his%20upper%20right%20ear%20but%20that%20he%20is%20otherwise%20doing%20well%20and%20would%20travel%20to%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention%20in%20Milwaukee%2C%20where%20he%20will%20receive%20his%20party's%20presidential%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMike%20Johnson%2C%20speaker%20of%20the%20Republican-controlled%20US%20House%20of%20Representatives%2C%20said%20panels%20in%20the%20chamber%20will%20call%20officials%20from%20the%20Secret%20Service%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20and%20the%20FBI%20for%20hearings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20American%20people%20deserve%20to%20know%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20House%20oversight%20panel%20called%20Secret%20Service%20Director%20Kimberly%20Cheatle%20to%20testify%20on%20July%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Service%2C%20tasked%20with%20protecting%20current%20and%20former%20presidents%2C%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security.%20The%20department's%20Office%20of%20the%20Inspector%20General%20is%20responsible%20for%20conducting%20oversight%20of%20Secret%20Service%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesman%20for%20the%20inspector%20general's%20office%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20questions%20about%20whether%20it%20would%20launch%20its%20own%20inquiry.%20The%20FBI%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20following%20the%20shooting%20that%20it%20would%20be%20the%20lead%20federal%20law%20enforcement%20agency%20in%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Secret%20Service%20spokesman%20Anthony%20Guglielmi%20said%20the%20agency%20had%20%26quot%3Badded%20protective%20resources%20(and)%20technology%20(and)%20capabilities%20as%20part%20of%20the%20increased%20campaign%20travel%20tempo.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuglielmi%20denied%20accusations%20that%20the%20agency%20had%20rebuffed%20requests%20for%20more%20security%20resources%20from%20Trump's%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20televised%20remarks%2C%20Biden%2C%2081%2C%20said%20that%20Trump%2C%20as%20a%20former%20president%20who%20is%20the%20Republicans'%20nominee%20for%20president%20in%20the%20Nov.%205%20election%2C%20already%20receives%20a%20heightened%20level%20of%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20consistent%20in%20my%20direction%20of%20the%20Secret%20Service%20to%20provide%20him%20with%20every%20resource%2C%20capability%20and%20protective%20measure%20necessary%20to%20ensure%20his%20continued%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%2C%20a%20Democrat%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bdirected%20an%20independent%20review%20of%20the%20national%20security%20at%20yesterday's%20rally%20to%20assess%20exactly%20what%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20results%20of%20which%20will%20be%20shared%20with%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Democratic%20Congressman%20Ritchie%20Torres%20said%20that%20he%20and%20Republican%20Congressman%20Mike%20Lawler%20are%20planning%20to%20introduce%20a%20bill%20that%20would%20call%20for%20enhanced%20security%20for%20all%20presidential%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Full%20Rifle%20Kit'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaul%20Eckloff%2C%20a%20former%20Secret%20Service%20agent%20who%20retired%20in%202020%2C%20said%20agents%20would%20have%20surveyed%20all%20the%20rooftops%20with%20a%20line%20of%20sight%20ahead%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20person%20either%20concealed%20themselves%20until%20they%20became%20a%20threat%2C%20or%20were%20not%20a%20threat%20until%20they%20revealed%20their%20weapons%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Eckloff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20moments%20after%20Trump%20was%20injured%2C%20the%20former%20president%20was%20quickly%20surrounded%20by%20Secret%20Service%20personnel%20who%20formed%20a%20human%20shield%2C%20while%20heavily%20armed%20agents%20in%20body%20armor%20and%20toting%20rifles%20also%20took%20to%20the%20stage%20and%20appeared%20to%20scan%20the%20area%20for%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20whisked%20by%20the%20agents%20to%20a%20black%20SUV%2C%20and%20taken%20to%20a%20local%20hospital%2C%20according%20to%20the%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20supporters%20blasted%20the%20Secret%20Service%20as%20having%20failed%20to%20protect%20the%20former%20president.%20Billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%20called%20for%20the%20agency's%20leadership%20to%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20was%20a%20sniper%20with%20a%20full%20rifle%20kit%20allowed%20to%20bear%20crawl%20onto%20the%20closest%20roof%20to%20a%20presidential%20nominee%2C%26quot%3B%20asked%20conservative%20activist%20Jack%20Posobiec%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20an%20intensive%20review%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20massive%20realignment%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Joseph%20LaSorsa%2C%20a%20former%20Secret%20Service%20agent%20who%20served%20on%20the%20presidential%20detail.%20%26quot%3BThis%20cannot%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecuring%20Trump%20Rallies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20most%20of%20Trump's%20campaign%20stops%2C%20local%20police%20aid%20the%20Secret%20Service%20in%20securing%20the%20venue.%20Agents%20from%20other%20agencies%20within%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Transportation%20Security%20Administration%2C%20occasionally%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20Trump%20rallies%20feature%20thousands%20of%20audience%20members%2C%20take%20place%20in%20the%20open%20air%20and%20last%20for%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20event%2C%20agents%20scan%20the%20venue%20for%20bombs%20or%20other%20threats%2C%20and%20Trump%20invariably%20arrives%20in%20a%20fortified%20motorcade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaw%20enforcement%20officials%20typically%20put%20up%20barriers%20as%20a%20perimeter%2C%20and%20require%20all%20attendees%20to%20go%20through%20a%20metal%20detector%20to%20enter%20the%20venue.%20Armed%20protective%20agents%20search%20all%20attendees'%20bags%20and%20even%20wallets.%2