plans%20to%20call%20on%20Americans%20to%20come%20together%20and%20end%20political%20violence%2C%20a%20campaign%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20place%20in%20America%20for%20this%20kind%20of%20violence%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20told%20reporters%20on%20Sunday%20at%20the%20White%20House.%20%26quot%3BUnity%20is%20the%20most%20elusive%20goal%20of%20all%2C%20but%20nothing%20is%20as%20important%20than%20that%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intense%20focus%20on%20the%20attempted%20assassination%20does%20offer%20Biden%20a%20reprieve%20from%20the%20conversation%20that%20had%20dominated%20headlines%20for%20weeks%3A%20whether%20he%20should%20withdraw%20after%20his%20disastrous%20debate.%20One%20Democratic%20donor%2C%20speaking%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20said%20that%20they%20previously%20believed%20the%20party%20would%20be%20best%20served%20by%20replacing%20Biden%2C%20but%20there's%20no%20way%20that%20could%20happen%20now%20without%20contributing%20to%20a%20sense%20of%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shooting%20-%20and%20Trump's%20iconic%2C%20bloodied%2C%20fist-pumping%20response%20-%20seems%20certain%20to%20rally%20voters%20and%20donors%20behind%20the%20Republican%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20leaders%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20Bill%20Ackman%2C%20who%20previously%20resisted%20endorsing%20the%20former%20president%2C%20came%20out%20with%20public%20statements%20backing%20Trump%20within%20minutes%20of%20his%20being%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20days%20or%20weeks%20before%20public%20opinion%20surveys%20are%20released%20assessing%20the%20aftermath.%20But%20former%20President%20Ronald%20Reagan%20saw%20a%20substantial%20increase%20in%20support%20when%20he%20was%20shot%20and%20wounded%20in%201981.%20Many%20presidential%20historians%20say%20that%20attack%20cemented%20his%20status%20in%20the%20conservative%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%20Biden%20must%20balance%20how%20to%20push%20forward%20without%20seeming%20insensitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20plans%20to%20reiterate%20his%20condemnation%20of%20violence%20in%20politics%20on%20Monday%20in%20a%20prime-time%20interview%20with%20NBC%20News%2C%20then%20his%20political%20operation%20will%20pivot%20back%20to%20drawing%20contrasts%20between%20Biden's%20vision%20and%20Trump's%2C%20the%20campaign%20official%20said.%20Biden%20will%20not%20shy%20away%20from%20talking%20about%20the%20stakes%20of%20the%20election%2C%20and%20his%20campaign%20sees%20the%20tragedy%20in%20Pennsylvania%20as%20reinforcing%20the%20central%20thesis%20of%20his%20campaign%2C%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20expressed%20sympathy%20for%20Trump%20on%20Sunday%20while%20vowing%20a%20%26quot%3Bthorough%20and%20swift%26quot%3B%20federal%20investigation%2C%20a%20Secret%20Service%20probe%20into%20its%20security%20measures%20and%20an%20independent%20review%20of%20the%20shooting%20that%20he%20pledged%20to%20release%20to%20the%20American%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20urged%20people%20not%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20assumptions%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20gunman's%20%26quot%3Bmotives%20or%20his%20affiliations%2C%26quot%3B%20imploring%20the%20public%20to%20%26quot%3Blet%20the%20FBI%20do%20their%20job%2C%20and%20their%20partner%20agencies%20do%20their%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Election%20Day%20less%20than%20four%20months%20away%2C%20Biden%20badly%20needs%20to%20reverse%20his%20standing.%20He%20trails%20Trump%20by%20nearly%203%20percentage%20points%2C%20according%20to%20the%20RealClearPolitics%20polling%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFigures%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20aisle%20have%20called%20for%20leaders%20to%20rise%20above%20the%20political%20fray%20and%20attempt%20to%20heal%20national%20divisions.%20The%20shooting%20confirmed%20the%20fears%20of%20half%20of%20swing-state%20voters%2C%20who%20said%20in%20a%20Bloomberg%20News%2FMorning%20Consult%20poll%20in%20May%20that%20they%20were%20worried%20about%20violence%20surrounding%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20the%20president's%20campaign%20said%20it%20would%20pause%20messaging%20and%20television%20ads.%20Biden%20postponed%20a%20Monday%20speech%20in%20Austin%20to%20mark%20the%2060th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Civil%20Rights%20Act.%20His%20campaign%20canceled%20a%20Monday%20event%20counter-programming%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention%20in%20Milwaukee.%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20delayed%20political%20travel%20originally%20scheduled%20for%20Tuesday%20in%20Florida%2C%20according%20to%20a%20campaign%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20will%20not%20be%20off%20the%20road%20for%20long.%20He%20plans%20to%20travel%20to%20Las%20Vegas%20to%20address%20Black%20and%20Latino%20advocacy%20groups%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20Wednesday%20and%20sit%20for%20another%20interview%20with%20BET%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERepublican%20Criticism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20law%20enforcement%20officials%2C%20and%20Trump%20himself%2C%20have%20not%20ascribed%20a%20motive%20to%20the%20shooter%2C%20some%20Republicans%20have%20already%20made%20unsubstantiated%20claims%20blaming%20Biden%20for%20motivating%20the%20would-be%20assassin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20central%20premise%20of%20the%20Biden%20campaign%20is%20that%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20an%20authoritarian%20fascist%20who%20must%20be%20stopped%20at%20all%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20Ohio%20Senator%20J.D.%20Vance%2C%20a%20possible%20Trump%20running%20mate%2C%20posted%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BThat%20rhetoric%20led%20directly%20to%20President%20Trump's%20attempted%20assassination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupporters%20of%20the%20president%20pointed%20to%20his%20call%20for%20unity%20after%20the%20shooting.%20Biden%20said%20he%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bshort%20but%20good%26quot%3B%20call%20with%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20campaign%20official%20denounced%20the%20criticism%20from%20some%20GOP%20lawmakers%2C%20calling%20politicization%20of%20the%20tragedy%20an%20unacceptable%20abdication%20of%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20failed%20assassination%20attempt%20shifts%20the%20dynamics%20of%20the%20race%20in%20Trump's%20favor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20remarkable%20twist%20of%20fate%20for%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20glorified%20violence%20throughout%20his%20political%20career%2C%20from%20encouraging%20rally%20attendees%20in%202016%20to%20%26quot%3Bknock%20the%20crap%26quot%3B%20out%20of%20protesters%20to%20telling%20supporters%20to%20%26quot%3Bfight%20like%20hell%26quot%3B%20on%20Jan.%206%2C%202021%2C%20just%20before%20they%20stormed%20the%20US%20Capitol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBiden's%20inevitable%20ritual%20condemnation%20of%20political%20violence%20today%20(when%20it%20comes)%20will%20be%20insufficient%20and%20irrelevant%2C%26quot%3B%20posted%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%2C%20who%20ran%20against%20Trump%20in%20the%202024%20GOP%20primaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDefiant%20Images%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepublican%20pollster%20Frank%20Luntz%20said%20the%20shooting%20guarantees%20%26quot%3Bevery%20Trump%20voter%20will%20actually%20vote%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20Biden%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20count%20on%20that%20certainty.%20The%20biggest%20effect%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20in%20battleground%20Pennsylvania%20-%20a%20must-win%20for%20Biden%20-%20because%20that%20is%20where%20the%20shooting%20occurred%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20long%20and%20winding%20road%20for%20Joe%20Biden%20just%20became%20even%20longer%20and%20windier%2C%26quot%3B%20Luntz%20posted%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BThe%20shooting%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20will%20be%20significantly%20consequential%20in%20a%20way%20the%20shooter%20never%20intended.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Trump%20dominating%20the%20national%20conversation%2C%20there's%20little%20Biden%20can%20do%20in%20the%20near%20term%20to%20push%20his%20anti-Trump%20message%2C%20mend%20Democratic%20divisions%20and%20shift%20the%20dynamics%20of%20the%20race%20in%20a%20way%20that%20reassures%20skeptics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20got%20to%20help%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20at%20least%20for%20a%20while%2C%20with%20independents%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Matthew%20Wilson%2C%20a%20Southern%20Methodist%20University%20political%20science%20professor.%20%26quot%3BThose%20images%20showing%20a%20defiant%20Donald%20Trump%20with%20blood%20on%20his%20face%20and%20his%20fist%20in%20the%20air%20are%20better%20advertising%20than%20anything%20money%20can%20buy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOthers%20urged%20caution%20in%20overstating%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20moment.%20They%20pointed%20to%20a%20minimal%20shift%20in%20polls%20after%20other%20seismic%20events%2C%20including%20Biden's%20debate%20catastrophe%20and%20Trump's%20conviction%20in%20the%20New%20York%20hush-money%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenator%20Bernie%20Sanders%2C%20a%20progressive%20stalwart%2C%20expressed%20confidence%20in%20Biden's%20chances%20as%20long%20as%20he%20focuses%20on%20his%20plans%20for%20a%20second%20term%20to%20bolster%20the%20social%20safety%20net%2C%20slash%20drug%20prices%20and%20expand%20workers'%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20continues%20to%20talk%20about%20that%2C%20I%20think%20he%20gets%20reelected%2C%26quot%3B%20Sanders%20said%20on%20NBC's%20Meet%20the%20Press.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721010780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fpg7gshog_gunfire-at-trump-rally_625x300_14_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-rally-shooting-changes-bidens-plan-to-revive-presidential-campaign-6107578%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Joe%20Biden%20had%20just%20begun%20to%20turn%20the%20tables%20in%20his%20reelection%20bid%20when%20the%20attempt%20on%20Donald%20Trump's%20life%20took%20away%20his%20most%20powerful%20tool%3A%20drawing%20attentio