-unlocked-after-46-years-6103379%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20Rally%20Victim%20Was%20A%20Firefighter%2C%20Died%20Shielding%20His%20Family%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20spectator%20who%20died%20in%20the%20shooting%20that%20targeted%20Donald%20Trump%20at%20a%20Pennsylvania%20rally%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Corey%20Comperatore%2C%20a%2050-year-old%20firefighter%20and%20father%20of%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20lost%20a%20fellow%20Pennsylvanian%20last%20night%2C%20Corey%20Comperatore%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20state's%20governor%2C%20Josh%20Shapiro%2C%20told%20reporters.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20spoke%20to%20his%20wife%20and%20his%20two%20daughters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20victim%20was%20a%20churchgoing%20firefighter%20and%20an%20enthusiastic%20Trump%20supporter%20who%20%26quot%3Bloved%20his%20community%20and%20most%20especially...his%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJosh%20Shapiro%20called%20Saturday's%20shooting%2C%20in%20which%20two%20other%20spectators%20were%20wounded%2C%20%26quot%3Bshocking%2C%20for%20this%20Commonwealth%20(state)%20and%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20victims%20have%20yet%20to%20be%20identified%2C%20though%20NPR%20news%20affiliate%20WESA%20quoted%20hospital%20officials%20in%20Pittsburgh%20as%20saying%20both%20were%20local%20men%20and%20both%20remained%20in%20critical%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shooter%2C%20identified%20as%2020-year-old%20Thomas%20Matthew%20Crooks%20of%20nearby%20Bethel%20Park%2C%20was%20killed%20by%20a%20Secret%20Service%20sniper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Corey%20Comperatore's%20daughters%2C%20Allyson%2C%20described%20her%20father%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20best%20dad%20a%20girl%20could%20ever%20ask%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20someone%20always%20ready%20to%20help%20and%20quick%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20friends%20with%20anyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20media%20will%20not%20tell%20you%20