0exam%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655a45b24ca513d8242bf8ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222732%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20average%20age%20of%20CFA%20exam%20takers%20is%20going%20down%2C%20per%20the%20CFA%20Institute.%3Cp%3EMatt%20McClain%2FFor%20The%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMore%20undergraduates%20are%20signing%20up%20for%20the%20CFA%20exams%2C%20a%20series%20of%20three%20difficult%20tests.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStudents%20are%20doing%20it%20to%20change%20career%20paths%20and%20boost%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECFA%20registration%20numbers%20have%20dropped%20significantly%20since%202020.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECandidates%20taking%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-a-cfa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20world's%20toughest%20exam%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20getting%20younger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20college%20students%20are%20signing%20up%20for%20the%20tests%20to%20get%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-students-fight-hunger-games-style-for-top-banking-jobs-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleg%20up%20in%20competing%20for%20internships%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20jobs%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Chartered%20Financial%20Analyst%20Institute%2C%20which%20administers%20the%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-here-are-the-exams-chatgpt-has-passed-so-far-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECFA%20is%20a%20three-exam%20qualification%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20often%20regarded%20as%20the%20industry's%20most%20rigorous%20and%20prestigious%20certification.%20It's%20a%20prerequisite%20for%20certain%20roles%20in%20banking%20or%20private%20equity.%20Only%2046%25%20of%20those%20who%20took%20the%20first%20level%20in%20May%20passed%20the%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20one%20in%20five%20people%20who%20start%20the%20CFA%20process%20are%20students%2C%20Rob%20Langrick%2C%20chief%20product%20advocate%20at%20the%20CFA%20Institute%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Recently%2C%20the%20average%20age%20of%20candidates%20fell%20from%2024%20to%20about%2023%20as%20the%20number%20of%20undergraduates%20enrolling%20for%20the%20program%20increased%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELangrick%20said%20that%20more%20people%20prefer%20to%20start%20the%20process%20while%20they%20are%20still%20used%20to%20studying%20and%20are%20not%20yet%20tied%20to%20a%20full-time%20work%20schedule.%20And%20for%20students%20coming%20from%20less-known%20schools%2C%20the%20CFA%20designation%20stands%20out%20for%20employers%2C%20Langrick%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20increase%20in%20college%20students%20starting%20the%20CFA%20process%20comes%20as%20fewer%20people%20overall%20are%20taking%20the%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECFA%20Level%20I%20sign-ups%20first%20dropped%20in%20late%202020%2C%20given%20pandemic-induced%20cancellations%20and%20exam%20deferments.%20But%20the%20numbers%20have%20dropped%20significantly%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%20and%202019%2C%20an%20average%20of%20about%20162%2C000%20people%20took%20the%20Level%20I%20exam%20each%20year.%20But%20in%202022%20and%202023%2C%20that%20annual%20average%20dropped%20to%20about%2087%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfainstitute.org%2F-%2Fmedia%2Fdocuments%2Fsupport%2Fprograms%2Fcfa%2Fcfa-exam-results-since-1963.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECFA%20Institute.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ca3e423-23a7-45a2-8189-371b47fc3583%5C%22%3EHelpful%20for%20portfolio%20managers%20but%20not%20for%20bankers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20Wye%2C%20who%20graduated%20last%20year%20from%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%2C%20prepared%20for%20the%20Level%20I%20and%20II%20exams%20as%20a%20student.%20He%20thought%20his%20economics%20degree%20didn't%20cover%20enough%20applied%20finance%20for%20the%20kinds%20of%20jobs%20he%20wanted%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20getting%20partway%20through%20the%20CFA%20didn't%20change%20his%20trajectory%2C%20Wye%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20that%20it%20did%20not%20explicitly%20give%20me%20an%20advantage%20in%20searching%20for%20finance%20internships%2C%20as%20I%20believe%20prior%20experience%20in%20related%20roles%20might%20be%20more%20valued%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWye%20is%20now%20working%20at%20a%20multinational%20bank%20while%20preparing%20for%20the%20Level%20III%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20certification%20may%20be%20important%20for%20roles%20like%20portfolio%20managers%20and%20securities%20analysts%2C%20Wye%20does%20not%20think%20its%20value%20applies%20to%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinance-job-search-headhunter-database-private-equity-investment-banking-hedge-funds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinance%20careers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20investment%20banking%20or%20sales%20and%20trading.%20On%20the%20job%20for%20a%20year%20now%2C%20he%20hasn't%20found%20many%20peers%20who%20passed%20all%20three%20CFA%20levels%2C%20nor%20that%20there%20is%20an%20implicit%20expectation%20of%20holding%20the%20designation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20candidate%2C%20who%20is%20in%20his%20third%20year%20of%20school%20at%20Singapore%20Management%20University%20and%20is%20preparing%20for%20Level%20I%2C%20agreed%20that%20the%20exam%20is%20more%20helpful%20for%20those%20outside%20finance%20looking%20to%20break%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20student%20spoke%20to%20BI%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20because%20he%20is%20a%20summer%20intern%20not%20authorized%20to%20speak%20with%20the%20media.%20His%20identity%20is%20known%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20important%20if%20I%20didn't%20have%20access%20to%20finance%20at%20all.%20But%20if%20you're%20already%20in%20a%20finance%20major%2C%20then%20maybe%20it's%20not%20as%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20your%20career%20in%20finance%3F%20Email%20this%20reporter%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ashubhangigoel%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eshubhangigoel%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcfa-exam-age-dropping-more-college-students-finance-internships-resume-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721001602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669145e49caa6ed01e011749%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcfa-exam-age-dropping-more-college-students-finance-internships-resume-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22About%20one%20in%20five%20people%20who%20start%20the%20CFA%20are%20students.%20They're%20looking%20for%20a%20leg%20up%20applying%20to%20internships%20and%20full-time%20jobs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22shubhangigoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A120%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcfa-exam-age-dropping-more-college-students-finance-internships-resume-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Julia%20Alvarez%3A%20A%20Life%20Reimagined%E2%80%99%20Documentary%20Set%20to%20Air%20on%20PBS%20in%20September%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721000573000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FJulia-Alvarez-Corey-Hendrickson.jpeg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236071849%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Acclaimed%20writer%20Julia%20Alvarez%20will%20be%20the%20focus%20of%20a%20new%20documentary%20for%20PBS%20from%20%E2%80%9CAmerican%20M