22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20former%20Secret%20Service%20agent%20says%20authorities%20should%20have%20had%20a%20comprehensive%20%26quot%3Bsite%20plan%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20event%20space%20and%20surrounding%20buildings%20for%20the%20rally%20where%20a%20shooter%20fired%20at%20Donald%20Trump.%3Cp%3EGene%20J.%20Puskar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20survived%20an%20assassination%20attempt%20at%20a%20Pennsylvania%20rally.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20former%20Secret%20Service%20agent%20says%20counter-snipers%20would%20usually%20have%20%26quot%3B360-degree%20coverage%26quot%3B%20for%20similar%20events.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestigators%20will%20likely%20look%20into%20the%20event's%20%26quot%3Bsite%20plan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20Secret%20Service%20agent%20said%20counter-snipers%20at%20the%20Pennsylvania%20rally%20where%20a%20would-be%20assassin%20wounded%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20should%20have%20had%20%26quot%3B360-degree%20coverage%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20event%20and%20surrounding%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20how%20many%20they%20had%2C%20but%20they%20usually%20always%20look%20for%20360-degree%20coverage%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20Secret%20Service%20agent%20Anthony%20Cangelosi%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSo%20that's%20one%20thing%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20considered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-was-thomas-matthew-crooks-the-trump-rally-shooter-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidentified%20the%20shooter%20as%20a%2020-year-old%20man%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Bethel%20Park%2C%20Pennsylvania.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECangelosi%2C%20who%20is%20now%20an%20adjunct%20professor%20at%20the%20John%20Jay%20School%20of%20Criminal%20Justice%20at%20the%20City%20University%20of%20New%20York%2C%20said%20the%20primary%20question%20law%20enforcement%20w