r%20unique%20behaviours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%982000%2B%20farmers%20benefitted%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20challenges%20that%20they%20faced%20initially%2C%20Ayan%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20team%20consists%20of%204%20to%205%20dedicated%20members%2C%20and%20it%20took%20us%20about%20two-and-a-half%20years%20to%20develop%20these%20products.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnderstanding%20the%20behaviour%20of%20different%20animals%20and%20how%20it%20changes%20with%20the%20seasons%20was%20crucial.%20For%20instance%2C%20elephants%20and%20wild%20boars%20behave%20differently%20in%20the%20winter%20compared%20to%20the%20summer.%20We%20conduct%20pilots%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%202%20to%203%20months%20to%20ensure%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20our%20products%20over%20different%20seasons%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20challenges%20that%20he%20faced%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20information%20among%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20farmers%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20understand%20how%20a%20simple%20light%20could%20deter%20animals%20when%20they%20were%20experiencing%20significant%20problems%20with%20wildlife.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20we%20conducted%20numerous%20demonstrations%20and%20partnered%20with%20organisations%20and%20farmer-produce%20organisations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyan%20ran%20pilots%20for%203-6%20months%20in%20various%20areas%2C%20allowing%20farmers%20to%20see%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20their%20solutions%20firsthand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20hands-on%20experience%20helped%20them%20trust%20and%20adopt%20the%20technology.%20Additionally%2C%20there%20was%20a%20general%20lack%20of%20awareness%20among%20farmers%20and%20villagers%20about%20non-invasive%20methods%20to%20deal%20with%20wildlife.%20Many%20were%20inclined%20to%20use%20harmful%20methods%20to%20protect%20their%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIntroducing%20them%20to%20new%2C%20humane%20technologies%20required%20significant%20effort%20in%20education%20and%20demonstration%20to%20show%20that%20these%20solutions%20could%20be%20effective%20without%20causing%20harm%20to%20the%20animals.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuresh%20Majhi%2C%20who%20is%20a%20farmer%20from%20Bandhuabeda%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20owns%20a%20small%20farm%20where%20he%20grows%20mangoes%2C%20cashews%20and%20aamla%20(gooseberries).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlternatively%2C%20I%20also%20grow%20vegetables.%20The%20area%20is%20prone%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20elephant%20infiltrations%20and%20I%20was%20struggling%20to%20keep%20my%20farm%20safe.%20I%20heard%20about%20the%20device%20Parabraksh%20and%20spent%20some%20money%20on%20installing%20it.%20It%20was%20a%20great%20decision%20because%20the%20technology%20has%20not%20only%20scared%20the%20animals%20away%20but%20also%20helped%20me%20increase%20my%20income.%20Since%20the%20installation%2C%20my%20income%20has%20increased%20by%20Rs%2080%2C000%20due%20to%20reduced%20loss%20of%20crop%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC8uVAqPPATd%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC8uVAqPPATd%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3