f%20Rs%204%2C000.%20Her%20son%20was%201.5%20years%20at%20the%20time%20while%20her%20daughter%20was%20four.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20refused%20to%20eat%20anything%20and%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20to%20give%20her%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Edabba%20%3C%2Fem%3E(tiffin).%20I%C2%A0%20really%20had%20to%20try%20different%20ways%20to%20incorporate%20different%20nutrients%20in%20her%20diet.%20When%20I%20gave%20her%20dosas%20or%20idlis%20with%20the%20moringa%20powder%20or%20mint%20powder%2C%20she%20ate%20it%20with%20great%20relish.%20I%20added%20dals%20for%20protein%20in%20the%20powder%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20powders%20were%20also%20a%20smart%20way%20to%20use%20greens%20that%20got%20spoiled%20as%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20fridge%20at%20that%20point.%20Their%20guests%20were%20also%20sent%20home%20with%20these%20%3Cem%3Epodis%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20after%20two%20or%20three%20times%2C%20they%20refused%20to%20accept%20it%20for%20free%20and%20asked%20Sudha%20to%20start%20charging%20for%20her%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESudha%20shares%20that%20she%20started%20making%20these%20powders%20with%20Rs%202%2C000%20saved%20from%20her%20salary%20in%202016.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20she%20registered%20the%20company%20%E2%80%98Iniya%20Organics%E2%80%99%20and%20started%20doing%20it%20full%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_432339768_933899508403207_22989637245785898_n_1080-min-1720445753.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Iniya%20Organics%20has%2037%20kinds%20of%20masalas%20and%20spices%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_432339768_933899508403207_22989637245785898_n_1080-min-1720445753.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media