3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20images%20courtesy%3A%20Sudha%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720448911000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsudhaa-min-1720445265.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D355942%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Once%20a%20teacher%2C%20Sudha%20started%20experimenting%20with%20different%20podis%20and%20masalas%20to%20make%20her%20daughter's%20food%20tastier.%20The%20Coimbatore-based%20entrepreneur%20grew%20her%20experiment%20into%20a%20startup%20called%20Iniya%20Organics%2C%20which%20sells%20spices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355942%2Forganic-masala-spices-in-coimbatore-tamil-nadu-iniya-organics-business-podis-health-mixes%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2275%20Ponds%20%26amp%3B%20Counting%3A%20Started%20at%2017%2C%20This%20Man%20Is%20on%20a%20Mission%20To%20Revive%20Water%20Bodies%20in%20His%20Village%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20loves%20a%20revolutionary.%20But%20no%20one%20wants%20someone%20of%20their%20own%20to%20put%20their%20life%20on%20the%20line%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rambabu%20Tiwari%20deduced%20this%20early%20on%20in%20life.%20Thirteen%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20he%2C%20as%20a%20Class%2012%20student%2C%20set%20out%20on%20a%20quest%20to%20tackle%20Bundelkhand%E2%80%99s%20water%20woes%2C%20he%20never%20assumed%20that%20this%20decision%20would%20shape%20the%20trajectory%20of%20his%20life%20and%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENor%20did%20he%20expect%20his%20work%20to%20earn%20him%20a%20mention%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20radio%20programme%20%E2%80%98Mann%20Ki%20Baat%E2%80%99%20(27%20June%202021).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%2030-year-old%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332504%2Fwater-heroes-in-india-revamp-lakes-rivers-canals-solve-drought%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20hero%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20a%20moniker%20that%20he%20has%20been%20bestowed%20with%20by%20the%20villagers%20of%20Adhawan%20in%20Bundelkhand%20%E2%80%94%20emphasises%20that%20recognitions%20and%20accolades%20come%20secondary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20fuels%20his%20drive%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20lies%20in%20the%20way%20Tiwari%E2%80%99s%20eyes%20light%20up%20each%20monsoon%20as%20the%20rains%20grace%20his%20village%2C%20filling%20up%20the%20rural%20ponds%20that%20had%20lain%20barren%20for%20years.%20Watching%20them%20spring%20to%20life%20is%20all%20the%20validation%20he%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20achieving%20the%20feat%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20easy%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20adding%20that%20sometimes%20the%20stubborn%20climate%20posed%20hurdles%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20relentless%20heat%20waves%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20with%20temperatures%20touching%2045%20degrees%20Celsius%20would%20cause%20the%20water%20bodies%20to%20run%20dry%20%E2%80%94%20while%20other%20times%2C%20it%20was%20his%20friends%20and%20family%20who%20were%20against%20his%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Tiwari%20has%20remained%20unfazed.%20And%20his%20stoicism%20was%20eventually%20met%20with%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20chat%20with%20him%2C%20we%20explore%20how%20this%20PhD%20student%E2%80%99s%20model%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296139%2Ftamil-nadu-man-quits-dubai-job-to-revive-water-bodies-help-lakhs-after-cyclone-india-water-warriors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereviving%20water%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20well%20be%20a%20gold%20standard%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20rural%20landscape%20that%20is%20struggling%20with%20water%20problems%20in%20the%20face%20of%20changing%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAs%20precious%20as%20gold%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nursery%20rhymes%20we%20grew%20up%20hearing%20are%20rooted%20in%20our%20memories.%20Likewise%20for%20Tiwari%20and%20the%20children%20of%20his%20village%3B%20albeit%20the%20rhymes%20were%20slightly%20different.%20Veering%20away%20from%20the%20popular%20ones%2C%20these%20verses%20emphasised%20the%20crucial%20importance%20of%20water%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDhaura%20tera%20paanee%20gajab%20kari%20jae%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3Egagaree%20(matakee)%20na%20phootai%2C%20khasam%20(pati)%20maree%20jae.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETranslating%20these%20lines%2C%20and%20underscoring%20their%20meaning%2C%20Tiwari%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20%5Bthe%20rhyme%5D%20originated%20centuries%20ago%20when%20the%20women%20of%20the%20village%20would%20walk%20for%20miles%20to%20fetch%20water%20from%20a%20certain%20pond.%20The%20water%20was%20considered%20so%20prized%20and%20expensive%20that%20the%20women%20would%20often%20pray%20to%20God%20to%20not%20let%20the%20%3Cem%3Ematkas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mud%20pots)%20crack%20and%20tell%20Him%20that%20He%20could%20take%20away%20their%20husbands%20instead.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rhyme%2C%20though%20morbid%2C%20encapsulates%20the%20pedestal%20on%20which%20water%20was%20put%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages--1720083198.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rambabu%20Tiwari's%20pond%20revival%20projects%20are%20targeted%20at%20mobilising%20community%20efforts.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages--1720083198.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages--1720083198-300x157.jpg%20300w%